

Hangman

Current scope

    no need to change view to table view
    read all 1k or more words from a file
    select a random word from the list
    update the used word list with selected random word
    scramble a random word to get rid of random no. of charcters
    make a decision to hide charactors based on the length of a random word
    next prompt a question for user to only enter a ONE character
    


Future revisions

    launch keyboard for user to input
    hint button to show a image to guess a word
    allow 2 or more players to participate
    q : how 2 players from own device see same contents and how those contents are kept in sync



